title: ArtBin 6979AB Magnetic Die Sheet Set 3-Pack, Die Organizers, Magnetic Organizer Sheets, [3] Sheets, White
description: Keep metal dies safe and organized for all your scrapbooking and other paper-crafting needs using these three ArtBin magnetic sheets. They grip your metal dies securely to keep them from becoming jumbled or damaged, and they fit neatly in the ArtBin magnetic die storage case (sold separately). Make it easy to pick out the die you need with these 7. 5 x 9 inch magnetic sheets.
